            "title": "特朗普宣布阿斯利康部分藥品將降價 以換取三年關稅寬限期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普宣布阿斯利康部分藥品將降價 以換取三年關稅寬限期\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"679\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QTod9TrqB4bz7m.rz.Bakg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/e87bae80-a6b0-11f0-9f9b-ad640e0158dc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普宣布阿斯利康部分藥品將降價 以換取三年關稅寬限期</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
